data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Located between Fremont, Bellevue, Tiffin, and Sandusky, this charming two-story abode is a true gem. 3-D metal roof (100-year transferable warranty), a testament to quality and durability, ensuring peace of mind for generations to come. Step inside, and you'll discover a home designed to be enjoyed in every season. Boasting four bedrooms and two full bathrooms, this residence offers the perfect balance of functionality and elegance. To add an extra layer of assurance, this home comes with a 1-year home warranty. Schedule your private tour today!
